                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing soluble dietary fibers through solid state fermentation of wheat bran",
                    "小麦麸皮固态发酵制备可溶性膳食纤维的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the field of soluble dietary fibers, and particularly relates to a method for preparing soluble dietary fibers through solid-state fermentation of wheat bran. The preparation method comprises the following steps: performing solid-state fermentation, ultrasonic extraction, centrifugal separation, low-temperature standing, filtration and drying on wheat bran, neurospora good, an auxiliary carbon source, a nitrogen source and inorganic salt to obtain soluble dietary fibers; the preparation method is based on nucleophilic addition between sulfydryl (R-SH) and amino (R-NH2); in the reaction, sulfur atoms of sulfydryl attack nitrogen atoms of amino to form C-S bonds and nitrogen (N2) molecules, and hydrogen ions (H &lt; + &gt;) are released at the same time; the 3-mercapto-2-butanone gas contains keto groups, so that after the 3-mercapto-2-butanone gas reacts with amino groups, the generated butanone group-containing soluble dietary fibers have special fragrance, and the fragrance can improve the mouth feel of the dietary fibers, so that the dietary fibers are easier to eat and more delicious."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于可溶性膳食纤维领域，具体关于一种小麦麸皮固态发酵制备可溶性膳食纤维的方法。本发明采用小麦麸皮、好食脉孢菌、辅助性碳源、氮源、无机盐，进行固态发酵，超声提取，离心分离，低温静置，过滤，干燥，得到可溶性膳食纤维；本发明基于巯基(R‑SH)和氨基(R‑NH2)之间的亲核加成；在反应中，巯基的硫原子进攻氨基的氮原子，形成C‑S键和氮气(N2)分子，同时释放出氢离子(H+)；由于3‑巯基‑2‑丁酮气体中含有酮基，因此与氨基反应后，生成的含丁酮基可溶性膳食纤维具有特有的香味，这种香味可以改善膳食纤维的口感，使其更易食用和可口。"
                }
            ]
